Dorgan, D-N.D., is 57. Rock singer-musician Jack Bruce (Cream) is 
56. Movie producer George Lucas (``Star Wars'') is 55. Actress Meg 
Foster is 51. Actress Season Hubley is 48. Rock singer David Byrne 
is 47. Movie director Robert Zemeckis is 47. Actor Tim Roth is 38. 
