commerce agreements during its third fiscal quarter ended April 30 
and surpassed Yahoo! to become the leading Internet portal by 
reaching nearly 32 million monthly visitors. Jefferies &AMP; Co. 
upgraded Lycos, but Needham &AMP; Co. downgraded it. 

</P>
<P>
	UniView Technologies Corp., down 5/16 at 2 29/32.  
</P>
<P>
	The information technologies consultant posted a third-quarter  
net loss of 19 cents a share, compared with a loss of 70 cents a 
year ago. The company expects continued revenue growth from 
recently announced agreements with major telecommunications 
companies. 

