<HEADLINE> Stock Prices Rise in London / British Stocks  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LONDON (AP) -- Share prices on the London Stock Exchange were  
higher at midday Thursday. 
</P>
<P>
	The Financial Times-Stock Exchange 100-share index was up 60.0  
points at 6,403.1. 
</P>
</TEXT>
