<P>
	14. ``Rugrats'' (Wednesday, 7:30 p.m.), Nickelodeon, 2.2, 2.19  
million homes. 
</P>
<P>
	15. ``WCW Monday Nitro Live!'' (Monday, 10 p.m.), TNT, 2.1, 2.13  
million homes. 


</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
