<HEADLINE> AP Corrects Pearl Jam-Kosovo Story </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	ATLANTA (AP) -- The Associated Press, in a story Wednesday about  
Pearl Jam's donating proceeds from its new ``Last Kiss'' single to 
aid Kosovo refugees, reported erroneously that the song will be on 
a Pearl Jam album. 
</P>
<P>
	The album, ``No Boundaries,'' is a compilation of songs by  
various artists. Epic Records said it created the album, to be 
released June 15, to benefit the refugees. 
</P>
